name: Car Diagnosis
query:
SELECT
    `tabCar Diagnosis`.`subject` as `Subject:data:150`,
    `tabCar Diagnosis`.`assigned_to` as `Assigned To:link:150`,
    `tabCar Diagnosis`.`priority` as `Priority To:rating:150`,
    `tabCar Diagnosis`.`date_of_receipt` as `Date of Receipt To:date:150`,
    `tabCar Diagnosis`.`customer_name` as `Customer_name To:link:150`,
    `tabCar Diagnosis`.`mobile` as `Mobile:data:150`,
    `tabCar Diagnosis`.`approver` as `Approver:link:150`,
    `tabCar Diagnosis`.`workflow_state` as `Workflow State:data:150` 
    FROM    
        `tabCar Diagnosis`
